articles.summary: PR Newswire: /C O R R E C T I O N -- XLCS Partners, Inc./. XLCS Partners, Inc., a leading middle-market investment bank, is pleased to announce it served as the exclusive advisor to The Window Experts (formerly known as Houston Window Experts) on its partnership with Mosaic Service Partners, a residential window and door replacement platform backed by Alpine Investors.
